05:58.040 --> 06:01.440
The Morgan type character was a staple of the family sitcom, being the adorable little

06:01.440 --> 06:04.080
kid who would come in to deliver a few cute one-liners.

06:04.080 --> 06:07.240
Hey, go to the game with my sister and her doll!

